  <brief_title>Pulmonary Rehabilitation in Patients Before Lung Transplantation (LTx)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of a Complex Pulmonary Rehabilitation Program on Patients With End Stage Lung Diseases Undergoing Evaluation for Lung Transplantation (Pre-LTx)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
